            <p class="comment-content">一份流落在东洋的「国故」。不过这书不是日本茶道入门，更不是茶道百科全书，而只是「茶之书」</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="796057350">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-796057350" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-796057350" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="796057350">有用</a>
